; printing object ENDGCODE
G4 ; wait
M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan
G1 Z34.4 ; Move print head up
G1 X0 Y200 F3000 ; home X axis
M84 ; disable motors
M300 S100 P10 ; chirp
M73 P100 R0
